{"tid":2506532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"七男女涉包圍沙田警署案 女督察潘小宇自以為法律專家不斷誇大及俾意見","createTime":"2021-04-27T11:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T13:10:07.000Z","uid":56115,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"79b8f2f1afad52bc42dda81c7ae6ee81aa0be27d","tid":2506532,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:14:25.000Z","msg":"前年反送中抗爭運動警民衝突不斷，多間警署被圍堵。其中8月11日晚上，過百名示威者聚集沙田警署外，警員多次施放催淚彈，驅散期間拘捕六男一女，控以非法集結等罪名。案件今在沙田裁判法院續審。昨日作供期間向裁判官稱「我又要講粗口了」的女督察潘小宇今日繼續昨供，其間多次與辯方爭辯何為「街坊裝」，又指示威者叫喊口號齊心，<span class=\"red\">形容「互助委員會都冇咁齊心」，認為示威者背後有人組織。<br />\n</span><br />\n辯方再問潘，當時警方頻繁發射催淚彈，一個普通市民戴口罩自保是否人之常情；潘指不同意，又稱「<span class=\"red\">一個唔犯法嘅市民，係唔會走向聚集人群</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n律師聞言謂：「我唔係問你點解影唔到，係問妳係咪同意。」潘遂答「同意」，但補充指現場有車輛響號，稱：「<span class=\"red\">你哋可能覺得係支持，但我哋會覺得係示威者行出馬路，車輛響號警告</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n有律師問潘，是否不能排除人群中有身穿街坊裝的市民在內，潘同意，但補充指「<span class=\"red\">街坊裝唔一定係短褲拖鞋，我唔明點解咁多律師同我講街坊裝</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n潘更一度企圖引述法例，惟遭辯方律師打斷謂「咁我哋唔知要抄到幾時」、「佢而家仲講法例喎」，提示控方「你控制下佢好喎」，控方遂指示潘「唔好岔得太遠」，潘隨即收聲。<br />\n<br />\n黑警潘小宇及防暴綠iphone合照<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs1.mingpao.com/education/20210427/s00012/9a59dd4ff154e2a0cb7381ac51edcd2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs1.mingpao.com%2Feducation%2F20210427%2Fs00012%2F9a59dd4ff154e2a0cb7381ac51edcd2f.jpg&h=ef35017c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2795b36c94e3c0e09cb8c01991132a1259a79faa","tid":2506532,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/FXAFWN4G6VBUDPUF3LFWQUXJ2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FFXAFWN4G6VBUDPUF3LFWQUXJ2M%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oNg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=b3268867\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210427%2FFXAFWN4G6VBUDPUF3LFWQUXJ2M%2F&h=fe12fb59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210427/FXAFWN4G6VBUDPUF3LFWQUXJ2M/</a>"},{"pid":"33b7feb8d53e0e4ea8d585f06ab8a9bffc147aeb","tid":2506532,"uid":44117,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"畜牲死全家"},{"pid":"51dc4358d46f6732dc11b11d832643096a6f3fdf","tid":2506532,"uid":55955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"一定係CIA組織啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d8b5a75fc6fa30df48689fd3fa847f5ce3e9a2","tid":2506532,"uid":166080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:18:48.000Z","msg":"黑警畜生死全家"},{"pid":"b8a3b73a4582fb1ab3e66d38b39ef7cff91691ba","tid":2506532,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51dc4358d46f6732dc11b11d832643096a6f3fdf","tid":2506532,"uid":55955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"一定係CIA組織啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"仲有Mi 6<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3b36d867efcb0d123177c5b3cbe114d3820751","tid":2506532,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"班狗唔係支那法律專家唔通你班外國勢力律師仔係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54997b19acaf3b0b9b8badd0e077bfd43fc58836","tid":2506532,"uid":2300,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:21:43.000Z","msg":"咩都外國勢力、有組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黑警入班就係咁樣洗腦"},{"pid":"a2eeaecd6fa863a1f726257fc6b7eca28086529d","tid":2506532,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:22:35.000Z","msg":"黑警"},{"pid":"479330c9cd2fb9a98da536a367059